I uninstalled when my daughter lost interest then later tried to reinstall and it won't download. I got a new phone and still won't download. Error message every time. This is the only app with this problem, so annoyed that I paid for something I can't use.

The time between the eggs that are supposed to be pressed is far too long for the attention span of the age of child this game is made for. I was watching my 2 year old play it and when it take as much as 20-30 seconds before the right eggs come up again she just gets bored and starts wanting to hit the other eggs. The developers tried to fix this by adding a speed setting but the problem is the frequency at which the right eggs comes up. That needs to be increased. Otherwise the game looks very polished.
Would be much better if we could select the words used however.
